What was good about todays lesson?

answer
It was good that I could learn more about words and words that I had heard before.
I gained new knowledges.
Every time I came across a word I didnt know, I looked it up immediately.
I was able to watch it over and over again until I understood everyones presentation.
I am happy because I listened everyones presentation.
Another peoples presentation was very interesting.
I think I could watch classmates videos.
I had a lot of tests at the end of the semester and I was very nervous, but I think I did my best in every class.
I got new knowledge and interest from everyones presentation.
It was interesting to hear presentations from so many people.

What was not so good?

answer
Some people didnt submit it before the deadline.
That was difficult.
I sometimes missed words.
There were times when I lost my concentration.
I am a little sleepy.
A few persons voice cant hear clear.
Im so disappointed with myself.
Classes started from the first period, and for the first time in a long time, I found it hard to get up early and go to school.
I cant see everyone because I dont have a face-to-face English class anymore.
